{"parse":{"title":"Consumer Financial Education Body","pageid":27117008,"revid":843895884,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Consumer Financial Education Body</b> (CFEB) is the former name for <a href=\"/wiki/The_Money_Advice_Service\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Money Advice Service\">The Money Advice Service</a>, an independent body that promotes personal <a href=\"/wiki/Financial_literacy\" title=\"Financial literacy\">financial literacy</a> in the <a href=\"/wiki/United_Kingdom\" title=\"United Kingdom\">United Kingdom</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>CFEB was established by the <a href=\"/wiki/Financial_Services_Authority\" title=\"Financial Services Authority\">Financial Services Authority</a> as required by the <i>Financial Services and Markets Act 2000</i> (as amended by the <i>Financial Services Act 2010</i>), and came into existence on April 26, 2010. The body has a mandate from <a href=\"/wiki/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom\" title=\"Parliament of the United Kingdom\">Parliament</a>, with all-party support, to develop consumer financial education in the UK and is responsible for enhancing the public\u2019s understanding and knowledge of financial matters and their ability to manage their own financial affairs.\n</p><p><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Tony_Hobman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tony Hobman (page does not exist)\">Tony Hobman</a> was named CEO of the new organisation, taking over on May 17. <a href=\"/wiki/Chris_Pond\" title=\"Chris Pond\">Chris Pond</a>, Director of Financial Capability at the FSA was named a senior advisor to both CFEB and the FSA. 134 FSA staff in the FSA\u2019s financial capability division were transferred to CFEB, located in offices at <a href=\"/wiki/Canary_Wharf\" title=\"Canary Wharf\">Canary Wharf</a>, London in its first year.\n</p><p>On April 4, 2011, CFEB was rebranded as the Money Advice Service.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Consumer_Financial_Education_Body&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cfebuk.org.uk\">Consumer Financial Education Body</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2228\nCached time: 20180921132702\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.034 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 383/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 97/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 396/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.004/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 525 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   24.281      1 Template:Reflist\n100.00%   24.281      1 -total\n  9.89%    2.401      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:27117008-0!canonical and timestamp 20180921132702 and revision id 843895884\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"Personal_finance_education"}],"links":[{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Canary Wharf"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Chris Pond"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Financial Services Authority"},{"ns":0,"exists":"",